cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques to analyze construction accident reports. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also a likely category as the paper discusses the importance of using digital safety reports to improve safety incidents in the construction industry. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possible category as the paper deals with safety incidents in the construction industry, which can be related to security. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning architectures for NLP to automatically learn injury precursors from text. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to analyze construction accident reports.
